      <h3>Top 3 Coffee Beans in the World</h3>
      <p>Here are three of the most famous coffee beans:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Arabica (Ethiopia) – smooth and sweet.</li>
        <li>Robusta (Vietnam) – strong, more caffeine.</li>
        <li>Liberica (Philippines) – rare with smoky flavor.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Each bean type has its own taste. At Cozy Bean, we offer different kinds so you can try them all.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>Why Coffee Makes You Happy</h3>
      <p>
        Coffee doesn’t just wake you up. It improves your mood because it helps your brain release dopamine, the “happiness” chemical.
      </p>
      <p>
        Coffee is also about the atmosphere: relaxing in a cozy café, talking with friends, or enjoying a quiet moment. 
        That’s why coffee is more than just a drink.
